{"id":634191,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/中国青年报-武汉开始集中收治新冠肺炎四类人/","date":"2020-02-04T17:41:59Z","modified":"2020-02-04T17:41:59Z","title":"中国青年报 | 武汉开始集中收治新冠肺炎“四类人员”","content":"<div id=\"attachment_634242\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-634242\" class=\"wp-image-634242\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员1-1-300x208.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"347\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员1-1-300x208.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员1-1-1024x710.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员1-1-768x532.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员1-1-1536x1065.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员1-1-2048x1420.png 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员1-1-1080x749.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-634242\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">2月3日，武汉市硚口区一家被改为新冠肺炎隔离点的维也纳酒店门口，来自各个社区的“四类人员”带着病历和生活用品等待入住。中青报·中青网记者 李峥苨/摄</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>中青报·中青网记者 李峥苨 见习记者 鲁冲 摄影报道</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>2月2日，根据武汉市新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎防控指挥部的要求，全市各城区都在进行“四类人员”的集中收治和隔离工作。这四类人员是：确诊患者、疑似患者、无法排除感染可能的发热患者、确诊患者的密切接触者。确诊患者集中收治，疑似患者集中隔离，发热患者、密切接触者集中隔离观察。</p>\n<p>武汉市集中隔离和收治“四类人员”，目的是有效控制传染源，坚决切断传染途径，坚决遏制疫情扩散。此前，因缺少试剂盒等原因，武汉市一些发热患者无法确诊为新冠肺炎，难以得到有效的隔离和救治，在一定程度上造成了潜在的交叉感染。医院发热门诊接诊压力大，病患居家隔离风险较高。“四类人员”集中收治和隔离后，将有效缓解这些情况。</p>\n<p>武汉市新冠肺炎防控指挥部要求，确诊的新冠肺炎轻症患者无法全部进入定点医院治疗的，必须征用其他医院或酒店作为临时治疗区，集中收治。疑似的新冠肺炎轻症患者无法入院隔离的，必须改造酒店作为临时隔离区，进行集中隔离。目前，武汉已有多家酒店被改造为新冠肺炎隔离点，隔离期间，各区免费提供食宿、医学观察和治疗。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_634243\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-634243\" class=\"wp-image-634243\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员2-300x201.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员2-300x201.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员2-1024x684.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员2-768x513.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员2-1536x1027.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员2-2048x1369.png 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员2-1080x722.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-634243\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">2月3日，武汉市硚口区一家被改为新冠肺炎隔离点的维也纳酒店门口，来自各个社区的“四类人员”等待入住。该酒店从2日开始接收各社区送来的新冠肺炎确诊和疑似病例，一些人接到社区通知后自行前来。 中青报·中青网记者 李峥苨/摄</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_634245\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-634245\" class=\"wp-image-634245\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员3-300x207.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员3-300x207.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员3-1024x705.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员3-768x529.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员3-1536x1057.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员3-2048x1410.png 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员3-1080x744.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-634245\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">2月3日，武汉市硚口区一家被改为新冠肺炎隔离点的维也纳酒店门口，来自各个社区的“四类人员”等待入住。该酒店提供免费住宿和一日三餐，入住前须测量体温。中青报·中青网记者 李峥苨/摄</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_634246\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-634246\" class=\"wp-image-634246\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员4-300x200.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员4-300x200.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员4-1024x683.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员4-768x512.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员4-1536x1024.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员4-2048x1365.png 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员4-1080x720.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-634246\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">2月3日，武汉市硚口区一家被改为新冠肺炎隔离点的维也纳酒店内，医护人员对隔离人员情况做详细了解并办理入住手续。该酒店预计接收150人左右，2月3日计划接收60人。据了解，隔离人员具体隔离时间将根据具体的医学检查确定。 中青报·中青网记者 李峥苨/摄</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_634247\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-634247\" class=\"wp-image-634247\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员5-300x200.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员5-300x200.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员5-1024x683.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员5-768x512.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员5-1536x1024.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员5-2048x1365.png 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员5-1080x720.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-634247\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">2月3日，武汉市洪山区，一名疑似感染新冠肺炎的患者携带行李准备上车。在其所居住的金色城市社区的协调下，他将去往4公里外的驿海柏曼酒店进行集中隔离。据金色城市社区居委会书记徐秋思介绍，该社区陆续有8名疑似患者去往各医院、酒店进行集中隔离，这名患者是第9位。中青报·中青网见习记者 鲁冲/摄</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_634248\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-634248\" class=\"wp-image-634248\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员6-300x200.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员6-300x200.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员6-1024x683.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员6-768x512.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员6-1536x1024.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员6-2048x1365.png 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员6-1080x720.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-634248\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">2月3日，武汉市洪山区，一名疑似患者到达驿海柏曼酒店后，医护人员对他进行酒精消毒。在出门之前，该患者在家还进行了自我消毒。中青报·中青网见习记者 鲁冲/摄</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_634255\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-634255\" class=\"wp-image-634255\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/640-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/640-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/640-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/640-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/640.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-634255\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">2月3日，武汉市洪山区驿海柏曼酒店，医生袁红在查看一名疑似患者的肺部CT，并告知病患“您目前的感染情况不严重，不要害怕”。该酒店的医生会根据疑似病患此前在医院得到的诊断，对其做大致的病情判断，并提供抗病毒、退烧的口服药。中青报·中青网见习记者 鲁冲/摄</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_634256\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-634256\" class=\"wp-image-634256\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/疑似患者-300x214.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"357\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/疑似患者-300x214.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/疑似患者-1024x732.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/疑似患者-768x549.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/疑似患者.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-634256\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">2月3日，武汉市洪山区驿海柏曼酒店，一名疑似患者在医护人员的护送下上楼入住。医生们会每天监测病人的体温和生命体征，并将疑似患者的核酸检测样本统一送检，检测为阳性的确诊患者将转移到定点医院治疗。酒店也有专门的消毒团队每天对酒店环境进行消毒。中青报·中青网见习记者 鲁冲/摄</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_634249\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-634249\" class=\"wp-image-634249\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员7-300x201.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员7-300x201.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员7-1024x684.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员7-768x513.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员7-1536x1027.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员7-2048x1369.png 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员7-1080x722.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-634249\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">2月3日，武汉市洪山区驿海柏曼酒店，医生林凯送完病人后摘下帽子，封闭的防护服让他满头大汗。据医护人员介绍，有些疑似患者会有心理上的恐慌，他们现在还兼职“心理医生”，对患者进行精神安抚。中青报·中青网见习记者 鲁冲/摄</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_634250\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-634250\" class=\"wp-image-634250\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员8-300x200.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员8-300x200.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员8-1024x683.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员8-768x512.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员8-1536x1024.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员8-2048x1365.png 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员8-1080x720.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-634250\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">2月3日，武汉市洪山区驿海柏曼酒店，医护人员在帮前来采访的记者进行消毒处理。中青报·中青网见习记者 鲁冲/摄</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_634251\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-634251\" class=\"wp-image-634251\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员9-300x193.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"321\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员9-300x193.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员9-1024x658.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员9-768x493.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员9-1536x986.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员9-2048x1315.png 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/四类人员9-1080x694.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-634251\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">2月3日，武汉市洪山区驿海柏曼酒店，正值交接班，医护人员一起鼓气加油。中青报·中青网见习记者 鲁冲/摄</p></div>\n<p>编辑| 曲俊燕</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CDS档案|<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E6%AD%A6%E6%B1%89%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E\">武汉肺炎</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-632597 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/wuhanfeiyan-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></p>\n","author":1067,"categories":[1,18271,38912,39707],"tags":[39646,39648,39720]}